Hi, our team uses MK4I with falcons. Our swerves stops in seemingly random times.

About our swerve:
Falcon 500s All up to date and pro versions
CANivore All up to date with 120Oh resistor at the end
We have current limits on our swerve
During driving our other systems dont use much power
When driving some of the canc oders turns red but we have no can error and it gets back to green when stoping
We tried replacing the other systems brakers with smaller ones but no cange

Take a look at the Cancoder User Guide

If it’s a fast blinking red, it means it has an error with finding the magnetic field. Dim if CAN has never been detected, bright red if CAN is fine. A slow red blink means CAN has been lost.
